text: Raffaella Memo (born 27 October 1964) is an Italian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Italy Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
